<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">النساء:</span> <span class="c2">(٨٢)</span> .<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">محمد:</span> <span class="c2">(٢٤)</span> .<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>كما في الآية <span class="c2">(٤٤)</span> من سورة البقرة، والآية <span class="c2">(٦٥)</span> من سورة آل عمران.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
